//Web Page that only contain string (1 line prob)

1) Install Python & PIP

2) Install Flask Framework
pip install flask

3) Create Flask application
//导入Flask模块，创建Flask应用实例
from flask import Flask
//在项目文件夹创建app.py的python文件
//referencing this file
app=Flask(__name__)
//Create index route
//When user visits /, call the index() function
@app.route(‘/’)
def index():
	return ‘GoHome’

4) Run Flask application
//When u run python app.py
if __name__ == '__main__':
//Start the development web server
 app.run()

5) Save & Close app.py

6) Start the app
-In command line，
Input==
python app.py
Output==
* Running on
http://127.0.0.1:5000/
* Running on

7) Access the URL
